6. Seeking of God in Ordinances, and working of iniquity out of them;
fits men have of good affections, but healthful constitutions of bad
ones.

                        Ans. I have been stirred up to preach the Gospel for the sake of that One;
and Ier. 3. 14. I will take one of a Tribe. Though all else be rejected, the
Lord minds thee.

